@startuml Leader Recruiter Dashboard - Very Simple

title Leader Recruiter Performance Dashboard\nMain Use Case (Very Simple)

actor "Leader\nRecruiter" as Leader
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Backend\nAPI" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Main Flow: View Performance Dashboard ==

Leader -> UI : 1. Login and navigate\nto dashboard

activate UI
UI -> API : 2. Request dashboard data
activate API

API -> API : 3. Verify user is\nLeader Recruiter

alt Not Leader
    API --> UI : Error: Access Denied
    UI --> Leader : Show error
else Is Leader
    API -> DB : 4. Get company staff\nand activities
    activate DB
    DB --> API : Data
    deactivate DB
    
    API -> API : 5. Calculate:\n• Job statistics\n• Candidate stats\n• Interview stats\n• Performance rates
    
    API --> UI : 6. Return dashboard
    deactivate API
    
    UI -> UI : 7. Display:\n• Summary cards\n• Staff list\n• Charts\n• Top performers
    
    UI --> Leader : 8. Show dashboard
    deactivate UI
end

|||

== Additional Actions ==

group Optional Actions
    Leader -> UI : Filter by date
    UI -> API : Reload with new filter
    API -> DB : Get filtered data
    DB --> API : Data
    API --> UI : Updated dashboard
    UI --> Leader : Show filtered results
    
    |||
    
    Leader -> UI : Click staff detail
    UI -> API : Get staff performance
    API -> DB : Get staff activities
    DB --> API : Data
    API --> UI : Staff metrics
    UI --> Leader : Show details
    
    |||
    
    Leader -> UI : Export report
    UI -> UI : Generate CSV
    UI -> Leader : Download file
end

@enduml





